OL,3,C'Dim the lights on Broadway' to honour
OL,4,CChita Rivera, says Catherine Zeta-Jones
OL,6,FCatherine Zeta-Jones has called for
OL,7,Fthe lights to be dimmed on Broadway in
OL,8,Fmemory of Tony-winning star Chita
OL,9,FRivera, who has died at the age of 91.
OL,11,FThe pioneering dancer, singer and
OL,12,Factress, died "peacefully" on Tuesday
OL,13,Fin New York after a brief illness, her
OL,14,Fdaughter Lisa Mordente confirmed in a
OL,15,Fstatement given to the PA news agency.
