OL,6,FRivera's agent, Merle Frimark, said it
OL,7,Fwas with "immense personal sorrow"
OL,8,Fthat she also announced the death of
OL,9,F"beloved Broadway icon" Rivera ` who
OL,10,Fhad been a "dear friend of over 40
OL,11,Fyears".
OL,13,FDuring her decades long-career, Rivera
OL,14,Fgarnered 10 Tony nominations for her
OL,15,Froles in Broadway shows including Bye
OL,16,FBye Birdie, Chicago and Merlin,
OL,17,Fwinning best leading actress in a
OL,18,Fmusical for her performance in The
OL,19,FRink and Kiss Of The Spider Woman.
