OL,6,FShe also received the coveted Kennedy
OL,7,FCentre Honour in 2002, and was awarded
OL,8,FThe Presidential Medal of Freedom by
OL,9,FPresident Barack Obama in 2009 ` which
OL,10,Fis the highest honour the US can give
OL,11,Fa civilian.
OL,13,FWelsh actress Zeta-Jones, who won best
OL,14,Fsupporting actress at the Academy
OL,15,FAwards playing Velma Kelly in the film
OL,16,Fadaption of Chicago ` the role Rivera
OL,17,Fplayed in the Broadway original ` said
OL,18,Fon Instagram: "There are no words to
OL,19,Ftell you what an incredible impact you
OL,20,Fhave had on my life.
