OL,3,C'Dim the lights on Broadway' to honour
OL,4,CChita Rivera, says Catherine Zeta-Jones
OL,6,F"From dreaming of being you as a
OL,7,Flittle girl, then meeting you and then
OL,8,Fbeing deeply connected to you by
OL,9,Fplaying the one and only Velma Kelly
OL,10,Fin Chicago.
OL,12,F"There will never, ever, be anyone
OL,13,Flike you Chita, ever. Dim the lights
OL,14,Fon Broadway! Or, may I suggest, we
OL,15,Fjust plug the plug. I love you Chita,
OL,16,Fsleep tight my Queen."
