OL,6,FMeanwhile Lord Andrew Lloyd Webber
OL,7,Fsaid "farewell" to Rivera on
OL,8,FInstagram, sharing a picture of the
OL,9,Fpair as they received lifetime
OL,10,Fachievement awards at the Tony's in
OL,11,F2018.
OL,13,F"You redefined the words 'theatrical
OL,14,Flegend'," he said.
OL,16,F"I'll never forget how we laughed
OL,17,Fbackstage before we got lifetime
OL,18,FTonys. I stifled hiccups through my
OL,19,Fspeech. I am truly honoured to have
OL,20,Fshared a moment with you."
