OL,6,FBorn in Washington DC, Rivera rose to
OL,7,Ffame in 1957 as Anita in the original
OL,8,Fproduction of West Side Story and was
OL,9,Fstill dancing on Broadway in 2015's
OL,10,FThe Visit ` which won her a Tony Award
OL,11,Fnomination for best leading actress in
OL,12,Fa musical.
OL,14,FTick, Tick...Boom! director Lin-Manuel
OL,15,FMiranda described Rivera, who made a
OL,16,Fcameo in the 2021 film, as a
OL,17,F"trailblazer" who has had many "iconic
OL,18,FBroadway roles because she was an
OL,19,Fabsolute original".
