OL,3,C'Dim the lights on Broadway' to honour
OL,4,CChita Rivera, says Catherine Zeta-Jones
OL,6,F"When we filmed the diner scene in ttB
OL,7,F(Tick, Tick...Boom!), she wasn't
OL,8,Favailable for the shoot dates, so I
OL,9,Fleft a chair empty in the diner for
OL,10,Fthose three days," he said on
OL,11,FInstagram.
OL,13,F"The whole shoot, people kept trying
OL,14,Fto move the chair or clear space and
OL,15,FI'd have to say no, we're GOING to get
OL,16,FChita, I don't know how but we're
OL,17,Fgoing to do it.
