OL,3,C'Dim the lights on Broadway' to honour
OL,4,CChita Rivera, says Catherine Zeta-Jones
OL,6,F"Eight months later on our reshoots,
OL,7,Fshe joined us and held court all day.
OL,8,FIt remains one of the all time joys of
OL,9,Fmy life. She was magnificent. She IS
OL,10,Fmagnificent, not ready for the past
OL,11,Ftense just yet.
OL,13,F"My heart is with everyone in Chita's
OL,14,Fgalaxy of family and friends."
OL,16,FThe funeral of Rivera will be held in
OL,17,Fprivate, while donations in her memory
OL,18,Fcan be made to Broadway Care and
OL,19,FEquity Fights Aids, her agent said.
